=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/pc_gaming_show.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/pc_gaming_show.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/pc_gaming_show.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/pc_gaming_show.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Future\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhere to watch:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/pcgamer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eYouTube\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/pcgamer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eTwitch\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pcgamermagazine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhen it starts:\u003c/strong\u003e Sunday, June 8, at 12 p.m. PST/3 p.m. EST/8 p.m. BST\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePC Gamer’s \u003cstrong\u003ePC Gaming Show\u003c/strong\u003e will show PC games — and nothing but PC games — on Sunday, June 8. Organizers say that this year’s PC Gaming Show will be “brimming with exclusives, announcements, world premieres and behind the scenes developer interviews,” viewers can look forward to over 50 games on PC, Steam Deck, Linux and MacOS this season of summer events and broadcasts—in the one and only show designed solely to celebrate all things PC gaming.” Some 50 games will be showcased, with publishers Ubisoft, Failbetter Games, Devolver Digital, and Astra Logical confirmed to appear.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"playstation-state-of-play-playstation-showcase\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003ePlayStation State of Play/PlayStation Showcase\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1280\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Artwork of the PlayStation “PS” logo on a stylized background\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24674044/playstation_showcase_may_2023_logo.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/